Source: casaos-official-container-store
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Hat Labs <info@hatlabs.fi>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/hatlabs/halos-imported-containers

Package: casaos-official-container-store
Architecture: all
Description: CasaOS Official container application store definition for Cockpit APT
 This package provides the store definition and branding for the CasaOS Official
 container application store, designed to work with cockpit-apt.
 .
 When installed alongside cockpit-apt, it enables discovery and installation of
 147+ auto-imported applications from the upstream CasaOS Official App Store.
 .
 Applications include media servers, home automation, productivity tools,
 networking utilities, storage solutions, and development platforms.
 .
 All apps are automatically converted from the upstream CasaOS App Store
 repository maintained by IceWhale Tech and packaged for HaLOS.
